<emphasis box="[214,326,404,428]" italics="true" pageId="68" pageNumber="69">Hydraena</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
<subSubSection pageId="68" pageNumber="69" type="distribution">
<paragraph blockId="68.[151,1436,151,500]" pageId="68" pageNumber="69">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[199,352,439,464]" inLineHeading="true" pageId="68" pageNumber="69" reason="1">Distribution.</emphasis>
Currently known only from the 
<typeStatus box="[713,761,440,464]" pageId="68" pageNumber="69">type</typeStatus>
locality, Mianmin, in the far western part of Area 1, near the border with Area 2; elevation 
<quantity box="[487,572,476,500]" metricMagnitude="3" metricUnit="m" metricValue="1.08" pageId="68" pageNumber="69" unit="m" value="1080.0">1080 m</quantity>
(
<figureCitation box="[587,683,476,500]" captionStart="FIGURES 483–486" captionStartId="396.[151,264,1650,1673]" captionTargetBox="[165,1421,252,1595]" captionTargetId="figure-23@396.[165,1421,193,1629]" captionTargetPageId="396" captionText="FIGURES 483–486. Geographical distributions of Hydraena species." figureDoi="http://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5284099" httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/5284099/files/figure.png" pageId="68" pageNumber="69">Fig. 485</figureCitation>
